<i>adjective</i>: 자상하다 [자상하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>자상하다 [자상하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. minute; full</dd><br>
<dd>꼼꼼하고 자세하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Meticulous and detailed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. considerate; attentive; thoughtful</dd><br>
<dd>인정이 많고 온갖 힘을 다하려는 마음이 깊다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having compassion for others and a sincere mind to do all one can for them.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>